#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int n,q,i;
	cin>>n>>q;
	string x,y;
	map<string,string>hash; //hashmap for matching trueNames to moniker
	for(i=0;i<n;i++)
    {
        cin>>x>>y;
        hash[y] = x;  //assigning a key,value pair
    }
    for(i=0;i<q;i++) //reading the queries
    {
        cin>>x;
        if(hash[x]=="\0") cout<<"Name not found"<<endl;
        else cout<<hash[x]<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
